languages.text: "Знаете, о чем мои думы? О том, как уютно в родной каюте с обогревом. С чем-то горячим в бокале. И под чьим-то теплым боком..."
"Want to know what I'm thinking about? I'm thinking about being in my nice, heated cabin. With a glass of something warm. And somebody warm pressed up against me..."

languages.text: “想知道我在想些什么吗？我希望能呆在我漂亮的、暖洋洋的小屋里，喝上一杯暖融融的饮料，再来个暖乎乎的人，把我紧紧地压在身下……”
languages.original_text: "Want to know what I'm thinking about? I'm thinking about being in my nice, heated cabin. With a glass of something warm. And somebody warm pressed up against me..."

traits.locale_text: “想知道我在想些什么吗？我希望能呆在我漂亮的、暖洋洋的小屋里，喝上一杯暖融融的饮料，再来个暖乎乎的人，把我紧紧地压在身下……”

languages.text: «¿Que en qué estoy pensando? En mi camarote cómodo y climatizado. Con un vaso de algo calentito... y un cuerpo cálido pegado al mío...».
languages.original_text: "Want to know what I'm thinking about? I'm thinking about being in my nice, heated cabin. With a glass of something warm. And somebody warm pressed up against me..."

traits.locale_text: «¿Que en qué estoy pensando? En mi camarote cómodo y climatizado. Con un vaso de algo calentito... y un cuerpo cálido pegado al mío...».

languages.text: 「私が何を考えているのか知りたい？暖房の効いた素敵なキャビンにいることを考えてるの。暖かいものを飲みながらね。そして、誰かが私にそれを手渡して…」
languages.original_text: "Want to know what I'm thinking about? I'm thinking about being in my nice, heated cabin. With a glass of something warm. And somebody warm pressed up against me..."

languages.text: "Wollt Ihr wissen, woran ich gerade denke? Ich denke an meine hübsche, beheizte Hütte. An ein heißes Getränk. Und einen warmen Körper, der sich an mich schmiegt ...!"
languages.original_text: "Want to know what I'm thinking about? I'm thinking about being in my nice, heated cabin. With a glass of something warm. And somebody warm pressed up against me..."

languages.text: « Vous savez à quoi je pense ? Je m'imagine dans ma cabine douillette et bien chauffée. Avec une boisson chaude quelconque. Et une peau tiède sous mes doigts... »
languages.original_text: "Want to know what I'm thinking about? I'm thinking about being in my nice, heated cabin. With a glass of something warm. And somebody warm pressed up against me..."

languages.text: "Ne hakkında düşündüğümü bilmek ister misin? O güzel, sıcak kabinim hakkında düşünüyordum. İçimi ısıtacak bir şeyler içtiğimi ve birinin sıcacık bedeniyle beni sarmaladığını..."
